<p><a name="Basic_concepts" id="Basic_concepts"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Navigation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Basic concepts">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Basic concepts</span></h2>
<table class="infobox" style="width: 20em;">
<tr>
<td colspan="2"><a href="/wiki/File:WorldMapLongLat-eq-circles-tropics-non.png" class="image" title="WorldMapLongLat-eq-circles-tropics-non.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/WorldMapLongLat-eq-circles-tropics-non.png/300px-WorldMapLongLat-eq-circles-tropics-non.png" width="300" height="147" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" align="center"><small style="line-height:130%"><a href="/wiki/Map" title="Map">Map</a> of <a href="/wiki/Earth" title="Earth">Earth</a></small></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background:#bbffee;"><a href="/wiki/Longitude" title="Longitude">Longitude</a> (λ)</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">Lines of longitude appear curved in this projection, but are actually halves of great circles.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background:#bbffee;"><a href="/wiki/Latitude" title="Latitude">Latitude</a> (φ)</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">Lines of latitude appear <a href="/wiki/Horizontal_plane" title="Horizontal plane">horizontal</a> in this projection, but are actually circular with different radii. All locations with a given latitude are collectively referred to as a <a href="/wiki/Circle_of_latitude" title="Circle of latitude">circle of latitude</a>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>The <b><a href="/wiki/Equator" title="Equator">equator</a></b> divides the planet into a <a href="/wiki/Northern_Hemisphere" title="Northern Hemisphere">Northern Hemisphere</a> and a <a href="/wiki/Southern_Hemisphere" title="Southern Hemisphere">Southern Hemisphere</a>, and has a latitude of 0°.</td>
<td><a href="/wiki/File:World_map_with_equator.jpg" class="image" title="World map with equator.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/World_map_with_equator.jpg/80px-World_map_with_equator.jpg" width="80" height="41" border="0" /></a></td>
