<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFNational_Imagery_and_Mapping_Agency2001"><a href="/wiki/National_Imagery_and_Mapping_Agency" title="National Imagery and Mapping Agency" class="mw-redirect">National Imagery and Mapping Agency</a> (2001) (PDF). <i><a href="http://www.nga.mil/portal/site/maritime/" class="external text" title="http://www.nga.mil/portal/site/maritime/" rel="nofollow">Publication 1310: Radar Navigation and Maneuvering Board Manual</a></i> (7th edition ed.). Bethesda, MD: U.S. Government Printing Office<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nga.mil/portal/site/maritime/" class="external free" title="http://www.nga.mil/portal/site/maritime/" rel="nofollow">http://www.nga.mil/portal/site/maritime/</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Publication+1310%3A+Radar+Navigation+and+Maneuvering+Board+Manual&amp;rft.aulast=National+Imagery+and+Mapping+Agency&amp;rft.au=National+Imagery+and+Mapping+Agency&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.edition=7th+edition&amp;rft.place=Bethesda%2C+MD&amp;rft.pub=U.S.+Government+Printing+Office&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nga.mil%2Fportal%2Fsite%2Fmaritime%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Navigation"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFTurpinMcEwen.2C_William_A.1980">Turpin, Edward A.; McEwen, William A. (1980). <i>Merchant Marine Officers' Handbook</i> (4th ed.). Centreville, MD: Cornell Maritime Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/087038056X" class="internal">ISBN 0-87038-056-X</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Merchant+Marine+Officers%27+Handbook&amp;rft.aulast=Turpin&amp;rft.aufirst=Edward+A.&amp;rft.au=Turpin%2C+Edward+A.&amp;rft.au=McEwen%2C+William+A.&amp;rft.date=1980&amp;rft.edition=4th&amp;rft.place=Centreville%2C+MD&amp;rft.pub=Cornell+Maritime+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-87038-056-X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Navigation"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
